			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Plan the Listen and Connect workshop. As you do so, take steps to reduce barriers to participation and empower participants.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Engaging people from all parts of your community is a ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Italic"
			text="must-have">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" for success. Workshops are a good way of bringing people from different parts of the community together but can also be difficult for people to attend. People need to feel included and comfortable in order to participate fully. Removing barriers and being intentional about inclusion will go a long way towards productive workshops and building relationships.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
				<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="18.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Work with a local partner, if you can, to co-plan this event">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Refer to your Community Engagement Plan to guide recruitment of a diverse group of attendees and offer a welcoming environment">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Use the Facilitators Guide to prepare activities and tailor them for your community">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Review your goals from your project plan and define objectives for the workshop to meet your goals">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Identify a facilitator to lead portions of the workshop">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
